hitman-sharpshooter-kit-name = Sharpshooter kit
hitman-sharpshooter-kit-description =
    A kit for those who prefer killing from afar.
    Provides a Hristov with ammo, thermal goggles and binoculars to spot
    your target, and a stealth box and cigarettes to pass the time while you wait.

hitman-bounty-hunter-kit-name = Bounty Hunter kit
hitman-bounty-hunter-kit-description =
    A kit for those who like a direct method.
    Provides a SKL93 and a python loaded with armor-piercing rounds, as well as
    an extra speedloader and a cowboy outfit, armor vest included.

hitman-assassin-kit-name = Assassin kit
hitman-assassin-kit-description =
    A kit for the quiet killers who want to blend in.
    Provides a Cobra with toxin and tranquilizer magazines, plus a set of
    chameleon clothing, agent ID, fake mindshield and an identity mask implant.

hitman-samurai-kit-name = Samurai kit
hitman-samurai-kit-description =
    A kit for those who want to fight up close.
    Provides a high frequency blade, throwing knives, a stim-pack and a scram implant.
    Plus no-slip shoes and samurai armor.

hitman-poisoner-kit-name = Poisoner kit
hitman-poisoner-kit-description =
    A kit for those who enjoy chemicals.
    Provides an advanced jet injector along with bottles of of Pax, Toxin,
    Mute Toxin, and Nocturine. A chemical synthesis kit is also provided.

hitman-saboteur-kit-name = Saboteur kit
hitman-saboteur-kit-description =
    A kit for those who want to get anywhere and ensure nowhere is safe.
    Provides a cryptographic sequencer, airlock access override and rapid construction device.
    Plus a set of tools and a dead man's signaller perfect for laying down traps.

hitman-tracker-kit-name = Tracker kit
hitman-tracker-kit-description =
    A kit for those who wish to know everything.
    Provides a master encryption key, binary key, spy monitor, camera bug, an AI detector
    disguised as a multitool, and a security hud disguised as sunglasses.
    Plus a modified station map that provides access to crew records.
